author: Lauren Murphy
title: MusicNews | Grimes announces headline date at Dublin's Olympia Theatre next March
text:
Fresh from supporting Lana Del Rey on some of her US summer tour dates, Grimes has announced a European tour next spring which takes in a Dublin date.
The Canadian musician will end her month-long 'AC!D Reign ' tour at the Olympia Theatre on March 15th.
The long-awaited follow-up to her third album ' Visions' is expected before the end of the year, so you can expect some new songs in the mix alongside the likes of ' Oblivion ' and ' Realiti'.
Support is from Hana and tickets are â‚¬30.90 including booking fee, and on sale from usual outlets this Friday at 9am.
